text: George Sargeant (born November 1997) is a British actor. He is best known for playing the role of TJ Spraggan in the BBC soap opera EastEnders. ==Career== Sargeant made his acting debut during a two part episode of the BBC medical drama Doctors as Ross Milton on 19 and 20 October 2011. Then in 2013 featured in a 28 episodes in the BBC soap EastEnders as TJ Spraggan between 7 November 2013 and 12 September 2014.
